OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776164568
OL,3,CTeens arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter pensioner's death
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after the death of
OL,8,Fa pensioner in his 70s in Cheltenham.
OL,10,FA 17-year-old boy and 16-year-old boy
OL,11,Fare in custody after the alleged
OL,12,Fserious assault which happened on
OL,13,FHoneybourne Way in the town on
OL,14,FWednesday 8 April at about 7.30pm.
OL,16,FThe pair were initially arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of causing grievous bodily
OL,18,Fharm but have since been rearrested
OL,19,Ffollowing the man's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
