OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776164568
OL,3,CTeens arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter pensioner's death
OL,6,FPolice say they were called to reports
OL,7,Fof an incident involving three males
OL,8,Fon Wednesday night.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "It was reported
OL,11,Fthat two males had been on the
OL,12,FMillennium Bridge and had thrown a
OL,13,Flarge branch at a cyclist who was
OL,14,Ftravelling on the road below. It is
OL,15,Fnot believed the cyclist was injured.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776164568
OL,3,CTeens arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter pensioner's death
OL,6,F"The males then left the bridge and
OL,7,Fwere approached by the victim, a man
OL,8,Faged in his 70s, on Honeybourne Way.
OL,9,FIt is reported an exchange took place
OL,10,Fbetween them before one of the males
OL,11,Fpunched the victim in the face causing
OL,12,Fhim to fall to the ground.
OL,14,F"The suspects then fled before
OL,15,Fofficers arrived at the location."
OL,17,FThe man was taken to Gloucestershire
OL,18,FRoyal Hospital after the incident
OL,19,Fwhere he was treated for his serious
OL,20,Finjuries. He died in hospital two days
OL,21,Flater on Friday 10 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
